### Rust ###
# Build artifacts for every crate in the workspace (root + nested)
target/
**/target/
# Backup files from rustfmt etc.
**/*.rs.bk
# Lockfile is committed only for binaries; this repo is a library workspace
# (remove this line if any crate here becomes a binary and you want a pinned build)
Cargo.lock

